OL,3,CPaedophile jailed for having half a
OL,4,Cmillion indecent images of children
OL,6,FA paedophile has been jailed after
OL,7,Fbeing found with half a million
OL,8,Findecent images of children.
OL,10,FGerrard Charnley, 52, downloaded
OL,11,Fmanuals on how to abuse children and
OL,12,Fkept a diary detailing his fantasies.
OL,14,FThe judge at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,15,Fsaid the material was "truly shocking".
OL,17,FCharnley, from Widnes, was sentenced
OL,18,Fto 14 months in prison on 2 January
OL,19,F2025.
