OL,4,Cmillion indecent images of children
OL,6,FJudge Andrew Menary, KC, the Recorder
OL,7,Fof Liverpool said that he may have
OL,8,Fonly been "playing out" his fantasies
OL,9,Fin writing his diary but "nevertheless
OL,10,Fit demonstrated the depraved perverted
OL,11,Fnature of your desires and reasons for
OL,12,Faccessing this material.
OL,14,F"It may be you have obsessive
OL,15,Fcompulsive traits and maybe you are
OL,16,Fsomeone who likes to create
OL,17,Fcollections of things even as
OL,18,Fhorrifying as this."
