OL,3,CPaedophile jailed for having half a
OL,4,Cmillion indecent images of children
OL,6,FHe told Charnley that collecting the
OL,7,Fmaterial had not been "an idle
OL,8,Fdecision but one where you are fixated
OL,9,Fon abusing children."
OL,11,FHe pleaded guilty to seven offences
OL,12,Finvolving possessing and downloading
OL,13,Fchild abuse images, possessing a
OL,14,Fpaedophile manual, prohibited images
OL,15,Fand extreme pornographic images.
OL,17,FForensic experts analysed the images
OL,18,Fafter his arrest on 24 February 2024
OL,19,Fand categorised 205,452 of them,
OL,20,Fincluding 17,000 in the most serious
OL,21,Fcategory of seriousness.
