OL,6,FJudge Menary said, "This court sees,
OL,7,Fsadly, many cases of this type but
OL,8,Fyour case compared to others is one
OL,9,Fwhere the nature of the material
OL,10,Frecovered and the content of the
OL,11,Fimages depicted is truly shocking."
OL,13,FHe said that Charnley had not worked
OL,14,Ffor some years and did not enjoy good
OL,15,Fhealth. "I suspect you were living a
OL,16,Ffairly solitary existence at your
OL,17,Fhome" and become "obsessed" with the
OL,18,Fmaterial.
