OL,6,FJudge Menary said that even if his
OL,7,Fdescriptions of what he would like to
OL,8,Fdo to children was fantasy there was
OL,9,F"a real risk" if he had unsupervised
OL,10,Fcontact with youngsters.
OL,12,FHe ordered Charnley to sign on the Sex
OL,13,FOffenders Register for ten years and
OL,14,Fimposed a Sexual Harm Prevention
OL,15,FOrder, which includes a ban on
OL,16,Funsupervised contact with children,
OL,17,Ffor the same length of time.
