OL,6,FMr Wilson said that the defendant had
OL,7,Fbeen open with the police and
OL,8,Fprobation "that he finds children
OL,9,Fattractive. He had been relieved when
OL,10,Farrested as he realised this chapter
OL,11,Fof his life was coming to an end."
OL,13,FHe added that there were no contact
